{
  "text": "Qualified genomic DNA samples were extracted from peripheral blood leucocytes of two affected members. The library preparation and exome sequencing, alignment of sequenced reads, single-nucleotide polymorphism and insertions or deletions calling, analysis for exomesequencing results were processed as previously described [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "14520392"
